ons%20since%20it%20entered%20service%20in%20the%20late%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EC-390%20around%20the%20world%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224263%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20C-390%20Millennium%20transits%20a%20runway%20before%20taking%20flight.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669ed65d80d4d5da13d6158e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222842%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20C-390%20Millennium%20transits%20a%20runway%20before%20taking%20flight.%3Cp%3EJakob%20Wert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20C-390%20acquisition%20by%20the%20Netherlands%20and%20Austria%20comes%20after%20South%20Korea%20%E2%80%94%20a%20longtime%20operator%20of%20the%20C-130%20%E2%80%94%20became%20Embraer's%20first%20customer%20in%20Asia%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20the%20country's%20Defense%20Acquisition%20Program%20Administration%20acquired%20three%20C-390s%20in%20a%20%24544%20million%20deal%2C%20or%20710%20billion%20won.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20C-390%20first%20entered%20the%20Brazilian%20Air%20Force%20in%202019%2C%20later%20joining%20the%20Hungarian%20Defense%20Forces%20in%202020%20and%20the%20Portuguese%20Air%20Force%20in%202023.%20Other%20countries%20have%20since%20been%20eyeing%20the%20C-390%2C%20including%20Sweden%2C%20Egypt%2C%20India%2C%20and%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20contrast%2C%20more%20than%202%2C500%20C-130%20aircraft%20have%20been%20ordered%20or%20delivered%20to%2063%20countries%20to%20date%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lockheedmartin.com%2Fen-us%2Fproducts%2Fc130%2Fhistory.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELockheed%20Martin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%2070%20countries%20are%20known%20to%20operate%20them%2C%20including%20Canada%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20C-390%20in%20development%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223605%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20C-390%20Millennium%20takes%20off%20from%20a%20runway%20during%20an%20airshow%20ceremony.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669ed65dfb2b6bedb0596d23%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222403%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20C-390%20Millennium%20takes%20off%20from%20a%20runway%20during%20an%20airshow%20ceremony.%3Cp%3EJakob%20Wert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDevelopment%20of%20the%20C-390%20first%20began%20in%20the%20late%202000s%20after%20Embraer%20was%20contracted%20to%20develop%20two%20prototypes%20of%20the%20medium-sized%20transport%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20third%20attempt%20to%20build%20the%20aircraft%2C%20the%20first%20production%20of%20the%20C-390%20made%20its%20maiden%20flight%20in%20October%202018.%20The%20Brazilian%20Air%20Force%20received%20its%20first%20C-390%20in%20September%202019%2C%20and%20two%20months%20later%2C%20the%20cargo%20plane%20debuted%20at%20the%20Dubai%20Airshow%2C%20entering%20the%20global%20market%20with%20a%20new%20name%3A%20the%20C-390%20Millenium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20C-390%20fleet%20in%20operation%20has%20since%20completed%20more%20than%2013%2C000%20flight%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERiding%20in%20the%20cargo%20hold%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20row%20of%20seating%20inside%20a%20C-390%20cargo%20plane.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669ed87780d4d5da13d615b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20row%20of%20seating%20inside%20a%20C-390%20cargo%20plane.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cargo%20hold%20can%20accommodate%20up%20to%2080%20troops%20or%20up%20to%2064%20paratroopers.%20The%20cabin%20has%20temperature%20control%20and%20reduced%20vibration%20and%20noise%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20complete%20toilet%20and%20heated%20floors%20for%20passengers'%20comfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMedical%20evacuations%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stacked%20cots%20are%20seen%20inside%20a%20C-390.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669ed8fa80d4d5da13d615c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221327%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStacked%20cots%20are%20seen%20inside%20a%20C-390.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20deployed%20to%20support%20ground%20operations%20or%20disaster%20relief%20missions%2C%20the%20Millenium's%20cargo%20hold%20can%20be%20configured%20to%20carry%20up%20to%2080%20stretchers%20to%20transport%20survivors%20or%20casualties%2C%20or%20less%20litters%20to%20provide%20room%20for%20up%20to%20eight%20medical%20attendants%20and%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHigh-tech%20avionics%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20pilots%20sit%20in%20the%20cockpit%20of%20a%20C-390.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669ed7b5fb2b6bedb0596d4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221442%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20pilots%20sit%20in%20the%20cockpit%20of%20a%20C-390.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20C-390%20is%20equipped%20with%20advanced%20tactical%20radar%2C%20threat%20detection%20systems%2C%20and%20aiming%20software%20that%20uses%20an%20algorithm%20to%20determine%20optimal%20drop%20points%20while%20giving%20the%20pilot%20an%20option%20to%20manually%20or%20automatically%20release%20cargo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20interior%2C%20exterior%2C%20and%20cockpit%20systems%20have%20night%20vision%20capabilities%20for%20night%20flights%2C%20aerial%20refueling%20operations%2C%20or%20low-vision%20search%20and%20rescue%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPitching%20the%20C-390%20in%20the%20US%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223241%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20military%20cargo%20plane%20flies%20against%20a%20backdrop%20of%20gray%20clouds%5C%22%20