20the%20International%20Olympic%20Committee%20(IOC)%20last%20year%2C%20also%20stated%20that%20Carini's%20federation%20and%20coach%20would%20receive%20%2425%2C000%20each.%20The%20incident%20has%20ignited%20a%20broader%20controversy%20over%20gender%20eligibility%20in%20sports.%20Khelif%2C%20alongside%20Taiwan's%20double%20world%20champion%20Lin%20Yu-ting%2C%20was%20cleared%20to%20compete%20in%20Paris%20despite%20both%20athletes%20being%20disqualified%20at%20the%202023%20World%20Championships%20for%20failing%20the%20IBA's%20eligibility%20rules.%20These%20rules%20prohibit%20athletes%20with%20male%20XY%20chromosomes%20from%20competing%20in%20women's%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20look%20at%20her%20tears%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Kremlev%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20released%20by%20IBA.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20indifferent%20to%20such%20situations%2C%20and%20I%20can%20assure%20that%20we%20will%20protect%20each%20boxer.%20I%20do%20not%20understand%20why%20they%20kill%20women's%20boxing.%20Only%20eligible%20athletes%20should%20compete%20in%20the%20ring%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20safety.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEralier%2C%20Italian%20Prime%20Minister%20Georgia%20Meloni%20also%20weighed%20in%2C%20noting%20that%20Carini%20faced%20a%20boxer%20with%20physical%20advantages%2C%20making%20it%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20fight%20between%20equals.%26quot%3B%20The%20controversy%20has%20led%20to%20increased%20scrutiny%20of%20the%20eligibility%20rules%2C%20which%20are%20based%20on%20those%20from%20the%20Tokyo%20Games%20in%202021%20and%20cannot%20be%20altered%20during%20the%20ongoing%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20everyone%20agrees%20with%20the%20criticism.%20WBC%20women's%20world%20featherweight%20champion%20Skye%20Nicolson%20defended%20Khelif%20and%20Lin%2C%20arguing%20they%20had%20been%20competing%20as%20women%20throughout%20their%20careers.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20not%20naturally%20born%20men%20who%20have%20decided%20to%20call%20themselves%20women%20or%20identify%20as%20women%20to%20fight%20women%20in%20the%20Olympics%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20stated.%20Nicolson%20suggested%20that%20Carini's%20withdrawal%20could%20have%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Bpublicity%20stunt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722673980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fgh280ib_sca_625x300_03_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fitalian-boxer-angela-carini-who-lost-to-imane-khelif-to-be-awarded-prize-money-amid-row-6253380%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20International%20Boxing%20Association%20(IBA)%20have%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20award%20Italy's%20Angela%20Carini%20%2450%2C000%20in%20prize%20money%20after%20she%20withdrew%20from%20her%20welterweight%20round-of-16%20bout%20against%20Algerian%20Imane%20Khelif%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fitalian-boxer-angela-carini-who-lost-to-imane-khelif-to-be-awarded-prize-money-amid-row-6253380%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fitalian-boxer-angela-carini-who-lost-to-imane-khelif-to-be-awarded-prize-money-amid-row-6253380%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fitalian-boxer-angela-carini-who-lost-to-imane-khelif-to-be-awarded-prize-money-amid-row-6253380%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20watch%20100m%20at%20the%20Olympics%20free%3A%20Live%20stream%20Sha'Carri%20Richardson%2C%20Noah%20Lyles%2C%20and%20more%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20wid