20missed%20out%20on%20a%20historic%20third%20medal%20after%20the%20Indian%20shooter%20finished%20fourth%20in%20the%20Women's%2025m%20Pistol%20event%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%20on%20Saturday.%20Manu%2C%20who%20already%20had%20two%20bronze%20medals%20to%20her%20name%2C%20came%20agonisingly%20close%20to%20assuring%20a%20medal%20for%20herself%20but%20was%20beaten%20by%20Hungary's%20Veronika%20Major%20in%20a%203rd%2F4th%20place%20elimination%20shoot-off.%20Both%20Manu%20and%20Major%20were%20tied%20at%2028%20after%20Series%208%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20both%20shooters%20competed%20in%20a%20shoot-off%20to%20decide%20who%20gets%20eliminated.%20While%20Manu%20had%203%20shots%20on%20target%2C%20Major%20ended%20up%20hitting%20the%20target%20four%20times%20to%20move%20forward%20as%20Manu's%20journey%20in%20the%20final%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20very%20nervous%20in%20the%20final.%20I%20was%20trying%20on%20every%20shot%20but%20things%20were%20not%20working%20out.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20always%20a%20next%20time%20and%20I%20will%20try%20my%20best%20the%20next%20time%20round%2C%26quot%3B%20Manu%20said%20after%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20qualification%20on%20Friday%2C%20Bhaker%20shot%20a%20total%20of%20590%20(294%20in%20precision%2C%20296%20in%20rapid)%20out%20of%20a%20possible%20600%20to%20reach%20her%20third%20final%20of%20this%20Olympics%20at%20second%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Bhaker%20had%20won%20bronze%20in%20the%20individual%2010m%20air%20pistol%20competition%20and%20then%20combined%20with%20Sarabjot%20Singh%20to%20claim%20another%20third-place%20finish%20in%20the%2010m%20air%20pistol%20mixed%20team%20event.%20Bhaker's%20second%20bronze%20had%20made%20her%20the%20first%20Indian%20after%20Independence%20to%20win%20two%20medals%20at%20the%20same%20Olympic%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Manu%20Bhaker%20and%20Sarabjot%20Singh%2C%20Swapnil%20Kusale%20won%20the%20bronze%20medal%20in%20the%20men's%