5Cn%3Cp%3EActor-cum-director%20and%20retired%20army%20officer%20Major%20Ravi%2C%20who%20accompanied%20Mohanlal%2C%20said%20that%20as%20managing%20director%20of%20the%20foundation%2C%20he%20was%20promising%20that%20they%20would%20rebuild%20the%20Mundakkai%20LP%20school%2C%20which%20stands%20in%20ruins%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20landslides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20making%20donations%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20Disaster%20Relief%20Fund%20(CMDRF)%20created%20a%20ripple%20within%20the%20Congress%20over%20the%20announcement%20by%20senior%20party%20leader%20Ramesh%20Chennithala%20that%20he%20would%20donate%20to%20it%20one%20month's%20salary%2C%20which%20he%20draws%20as%20an%20MLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20drew%20a%20sharp%20reaction%20from%20his%20party%20colleague%20and%20KPCC%20chief%2C%20K%20Sudhakaran%2C%20who%2C%20on%20Saturday%2C%20expressed%20displeasure%20by%20saying%20that%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20give%20money%20to%20the%20funds%20managed%20by%20the%20CPI(M)-led%20Left%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20directive%20(from%20the%20Kerala%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee)%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20government's%20fund%20(CMDRF)%2C%26quot%3B%20Sudhakaran%20told%20a%20news%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Congress%20was%20raising%20funds%20to%20help%20the%20affected%20people%2C%20and%20Chennithala%20should%20have%20contributed%20to%20that%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESudhakaran's%20statement%20comes%20amidst%20online%20smear%20campaigns%20discouraging%20people%20from%20sending%20funds%20to%20the%20CMDRF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20lodged%2039%20FIRs%20till%20Friday%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20smear%20campaigns%20against%20the%20CM's%20Facebook%20post%20requesting%20help%20for%20the%20people%20affected%20by%20the%20landslides%20in%20Wayanad%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20also%20said%20that%2C%20as%20of%20Friday%2C%20279%20