sual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F597ko6bs_freed-russian-spies_625x300_03_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fa-spy-couple-s-kids-had-no-clue-they-were-russians-till-they-landed-in-moscow-6252971%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Their%20parents%20were%20posing%20as%20an%20Argentine%20couple%20in%20Slovenia%20and%20were%20later%20convicted%20of%20spying.%20The%20two%20children%20accompanied%20them%20to%20Moscow%20on%20Thursday%20from%20Turkey%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fa-spy-couple-s-kids-had-no-clue-they-were-russians-till-they-landed-in-moscow-6252971%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fa-spy-couple-s-kids-had-no-clue-they-were-russians-till-they-landed-in-moscow-6252971%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fa-spy-couple-s-kids-had-no-clue-they-were-russians-till-they-landed-in-moscow-6252971%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Learnings%20From%20Collaborative%20Effort%20To%20Protect%20Democracy%20From%20Misinformation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20year%202024%20will%20be%20remembered%20as%20the%20year%20when%20more%20than%2050%20countries%20around%20the%20world%20went%20to%20elections%2C%20granting%20the%20people%20the%20right%20to%20choose%20their%20representatives%20for%20a%20democratic%20and%20an%20egalitarian%20society.%20People%20who%20have%20faith%20in%20democracy%20look%20up%20to%20elections%20as%20their%20Cap%20of%20Hades%20to%20protect%20just%20and%20free%20society.%20In%20a%20country%20like%20India%20where%20the%20internet%20penetration%20is%20high%20and%20social%20media%20plays%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20shaping%20public%20opinion%2C%20the%20proliferation%20of%20misinformation%20into%20the%20mainstream%20of%20our%20societal%20fabric%2C%20fuelled%20by%20lack%20of%20digital%20literacy%20has%20made%20India%20and%20its%20more%20than%20800%20million%20internet%20users%2C%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20information%20chaos.%20Ahead%20of%20India's%20national%20elections%2C%20we%20witnessed%20a%20rising%20tide%20of%20mis-and%20disinformation%20often%20aimed%20to%20create%20chaos%20to%20subvert%20the%20democratic%20processes%20and%20befuddle%20the%20political%20wisdom%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELittle%20wonder%20then%20that%20the%20Global%20Risk%20Report%202024%20from%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20highlighted%20that%20misinformation%20is%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20threats%20that%20countries%20around%20the%20world%20are%20faced%20with%20and%20India%2C%20the%20largest%20democracy%20in%20the%20world%2C%20was%20identified%20as%20one%20of%20the%20nations%20with%20the%20most%20significant%20risk%20associated%20with%20disinformation%20and%20misinformation.%20While%20at%20DataLEADS%2C%20we%20have%20been%20working%20towards%20protecting%20the%20information%20ecosystem%20in%20India%20for%20many%20years%20now%2C%20given%20the%20enormity%20of%20the%20problem%2C%20the%20languages%20spoken%2C%20and%20the%20regional%20diversity%2C%20the%20challenge%20to%20protect%20people%20from%20harmful%20and%20misleading%20content%20during%20the%20national%20elections%20was%20enormous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisinformation%20destroys%20people's%20faith%20in%20authentic%20news%20sources.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShakti%20Collective%20came%20to%20life%20with%20the%20realisation%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20a%20concerted%20and%20collaborative%20effort%20on%20part%20of%20the%20newsrooms%20and%20publishers%20in%20the%20country%20to%20put%20up%20a%20formidable%20fence%20against%20misinformation%20particularly%20at%C2%A0%20a%20time%C2%A0%20when%20the%20spread%20of%20misinformation%20is%20threatening%20to%20undermine%20the%20democratic%20process%20to%20an%20unprecedented%20degree.%20The%20Collective%2C%20launched%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Indian%20general%20elections%2C%20is%20by%20far%20India's%20most%20extensive%20collaboration%20to%20date%20between%20fact-checkers%20and%20publishers.%20This%20initiative%2C%20a%20consortium%20of%20over%2050%20Indian%20fact%20checkers%20and%20publishers%2C%20committed%20itself%20to%20foster%20accurate%20reporting%20of%20Indian%20elections%20by%20facilitating%20rigorous%20fact-checking%20of%20election%20related%20misinformation.%20The%20aim%20was%20to%20create%20an%20effective%20antidote%20to%20emerging%20trends%20in%20election-related%20misinformation.%20This%20crucial%20intervention%20not%20only%20helped%20fortify%20newsrooms%20and%20publishers%20towards%20creating%20an%20effective%20strategy%20to%20fight%20misinformation%2C%20but%20also%20lent%20them%20more%20capacity%20through%20training%20and%20resource%20sharing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupported%20by%20Google%20News%20Initiative%2C%20this%20coalition%20of%20Indian%20fact-checkers%20and%20publishers%20helped%20enhance%20the%20early%20detection%20of%20election-related%20misinformation%20and%20Deepfakes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20amplify%20the%20dissemination%20of%20fact-checks%20in%20regional%20languages.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImportance%20of%20Interdisciplinary%20Teams%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20initiative%20was%20built%20around%20an%20innovative%20framework%2C%20involving%20multiple%20stakeholders%2C%2050%2B%20diverse%20news%20organizations%2C%20including%20competitors%2C%20fact-checkers%20and%20technologists%20who%20came%20together%20to%20address%20the%20common%20threat%20of%20misinformation%20during%20the%20national%20elections.%C2%A0%20Every%20single%20day%20during%20the%20three%20month%20long%20election%20period%2C%20more%20than%20300%20fact-checkers%2C%20reporters%2C%20editors%20and%20technologists%20collaborated%20to%20identify%20misinformation%20and%20combat%20misleading%20content%2C%20bogus%20poll%20surveys%2C%20conspiracy%20theories%20mostly%20targeting%20political%20leaders%2C%20political%20manifestos%2C%20and%20election%20processes%2C%20including%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVM)%20and%20voter-verified%20audit%20trails%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20diversity%20of%20the%20involved%20teams%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20crucial%20differentiator%2C%20and%20ensured%20that%20be%20it%20automated%20alerts%20system%20or%20maintaining%20the%20repository%20and%20ensuring%20due%20compliance%2C%20it%20took%20every%20spoke%20in%20wheel%20to%20come%20together%20for%20the%20Collective%20to%20function%20like%20a%20well-oiled%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPower%20of%20Collaboration%3A%20Amplifying%20fact-checking%20networks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20a%20diverse%20country%20where%20each%20region%20comes%20with%20its%20own%20challenges%20with%20respect%20to%20tackling%20misinformation.%20This%20is%20where%20the%20fact-checkers%20and%20publishers%20in%20the%20Collective%20created%20a%20significant%20difference.%20Newsrooms%20got%20easy%20access%20to%20timely%20fact-checked%20stories%20that%20followed%20the%20International%20Fact-Checking%20Network's%20guidelines%2C%20and%20what%20took%20fact-checkers%20a%20few%20hours%20to%20debunk%20could%20be%20republished%C2%A0%20instantly.%20This%20saved%20newsrooms%20crucial%20time%20in%20the%20busy%20election%20season%20and%20aided%20in%20early%20detection%20of%20election-related%20misinformation%20and%20deep%20fakes.%20This%20amplification%20across%20diverse%20regions%20and%20languages%20helped%20protect%20millions%20of%20voters%20from%20poll-related%20misinformation%20and%20eventually%20played%20an%20important%20role%20in%20saving%20the%20integrity%20of%20elections%2C%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%206600%20fact%20checks%20were%20distributed%20and%20amplified%20during%20the%20elections%20in%20more%20than%2010%20languages%2C%20which%20eventually%20resulted%20in%20the%C2%A0%2092%25%20increase%20in%20number%20of%20fact%20checks%20published%20and%20180%25%20increase%20in%20regional%20language%20fact%20checks.%20The%20remarkable%20success%20of%20the%20intervention%20was%20that%2067%2B%20new%20fact%20checks%20desks%20were%20activated%20by%20publishers%20in%2010%20languages%20across%20India%20where%20editorial%20teams%20were%20actively%20engaged%20in%20countering%20election%20misinformation.%20This%20election%20fact-checking%20effort%20has%20been%20supported%20by%20deepfake%20and%20synthetic%20media%20experts%20from%20renowned%20institutions%20such%20as%20the%20Indian%20Institutes%20of%20Technology%2C%20and%20other%20leading%20AI%20organizations.%20These%20experts%20emphasized%20the%20crucial%20role%20that%20tools%20and%20technology%20play%20in%20debunking%20misinformation%2C%20particularly%20Deepfakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIncorporating%20Language%20Diversity%20in%20Fact%20Checking%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20election%20taught%20us%20that%20no%20one%20is%20safe%20from%20the%20misinformation%20onslaught.%20While%20those%20that%20speak%20English%20have%20access%20to%20fact%20checks%20and%20verified%20information%2C%20the%20same%20is%20not%20always%20true%20of%20other%20languages.%20Regional%20Indian%20languages%20are%20often%20under-resourced%20by%20fact%20checking%20organizations%2C%20making%20it%20more%20difficult%20to%20tackle%20misinformation.%C2%A0%20India%20is%20home%20to%2022%20official%20languages%20and%20at%20least%20122%20major%20languages%2C%20making%20it%20especially%20difficult%20for%20fact%20checkers%2C%20to%20ensure%20everyone%20has%20access%20to%20verified%20information.%20This%20diversity%20acted%20as%20a%20natural%20barrier%20against%20the%20fighting%20mis-and%20disinformation.%20The%20spread%20of%20false%20information%20has%20had%20especially%20dangerous%20repercussions%20in%20the%20countryside%2C%20as%20misinformation%2C%20conspiracy%20theories%20and%20rumours%20have%20incited%20violence%20and%20mob%20attacks%2C%20leaving%20dozens%20dead%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Collective%20ensured%20language%20amplification%20by%20incorporating%20members%20from%20diverse%20regions.%20India's%20leading%20new%20agency%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20(PTI)%2C%20for%20example%2C%20publishes%20fact-checks%20in%20two%20languages%20but%20when%20it%20made%20its%20fact-checks%20available%20to%20publishers%2C%20they%20republished%20the%20content%20in%2011%20more%20languages.%20That%20way%20the%20fact%20checks%20reached%20a%20significant%20population%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%20Overall%20we%20witnessed%20180%25%20average%20amplification%20of%20regional%20language%20(top%208)%20fact%20checks%20(excluding%20Hindi%20and%20English).%20Most%20amplified%20languages%20were%20Kannada%20with%20a%20302%25%20increase%2C%20followed%20by%C2%A0%C2%A0%20Marathi%20(282%25%20)%20and%20Tamil%20(%20236%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELanguage%20plays%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20shaping%20our%20perceptions%20and%20behaviours%2C%20often%20in%20ways%20we%20may%20not%20fully%20appreciate.%20More%20often%20the%20speakers%20of%20different%20languages%20interpret%20the%20world%20from%20unique%20perspectives%20and%20that%20underscores%20the%20importance%20of%20promoting%20linguistic%20diversity%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20fact-checking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDetecting%20and%20addressing%20Deepfakes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20the%20synthetic%20media%20and%20Deepfake%20tools%20are%20rewriting%20the%20disinformation%20playbook.%20There%20is%20no%20better%20place%20to%20study%20this%20than%20India%2C%20which%2C%20as%20mentioned%20already%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20nations%20with%20the%20most%20significant%20risk%20associated%20with%20disinformation%20than%20any%20other%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20election%20year%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20usual%20bad%20actors%20like%20image%2C%20audio%20and%20video%20tampering%2C%20Deepfake%20has%20been%20seen%20as%20a%20potent%20enabler%20of%20these%20bad%20actors%20in%20shaping%20people's%20perceptions%20and%20rupturing%20the%20integrity%20that%20elections%20hold.%20Cloned%20voices%20and%20AI-generated%20images%20and%20videos%20of%20political%20leaders%20have%20become%20a%20prominent%20feature%2C%20often%20used%20to%20influence%20voters'%20decisions%20and%20consequently%20endanger%20democratic%20processes.%20But%20India's%20election%20wasn't%20infected%20with%20deepfake%20content%20many%20feared.%20The%20misleading%20and%20harmful%20content%20was%20mostly%20created%20using%20relatively%20cheap%20and%20simple%20techniques%20such%20as%20footage%20editing%20or%20mislabelling%20to%20present%20content%20in%20a%20misleading%20context.%C2%A0%C2%A0%20The%20biggest%20threat%20posed%20by%20disinformation%20is%20that%20it%20is%20not%20just%20fake%20content%20that%20makes%20people%20believe%20false%20things%E2%80%94it's%20also%20making%20them%20less%20likely%20to%20accept%20truthful%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20save%20the%20public%20from%20deception%2C%20the%20Shakti%20Collective%2C%20established%20a%20Synthetic%20Media%20and%20Deepfakes%20Advisory%20Council%20and%20created%20daily%20alerts%20for%20newsrooms%20across%20India%2C%20helping%20them%20to%20be%20informed%20about%20viral%20misinformation%2FDeepfakes%20related%20to%20elections.%20The%20teams%20monitored%20misinformation%20vectors%20online%20and%20built%20an%20online%20repository%20of%20risks%2C%20covering%2028%20Indian%20states.%20This%20eventually%20served%20as%20an%20early%20warning%20detection%20system%20and%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20identifying%20and%20debunking%20Deepfakes.%20Based%20on%20the%20survey%20conducted%20with%20Indian%20fact-checkers%20who%20have%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20in%20fighting%20misinformation%2C%20we%20conducted%20a%20special%20workshop%20series%20in%20collaboration%20with%20WITNESS%20and%20India's%20leading%20AI%20scientists%20on%20detection%20approaches%20and%20solution%20of%20deepfakes%20including%20Manual%20Standard%20Verification%20and%20glitch%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Blueprint%20for%20the%20future%20to%20make%20collaborations%20easy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20misinformation%20continues%20to%20batter%20trust%20in%20democracy%20and%20its%20allied%20institutions%20worldwide%2C%20the%20lessons%20learned%20from%20the%20Shakti%20Collective%20are%20more%20relevant%20than%20ever.%20The%20initiative's%20success%20in%20India%20provides%20a%20clear%20blueprint%20for%20future%20collaborations%20aimed%20at%20combating%20misinformation%20globally.%20By%20streamlining%20fact-check%20distribution%2C%20pooling%20resources%2C%20fostering%20interdisciplinary%20teams%2C%20and%20supporting%20linguistic%20diversity%2C%20similar%20projects%20can%20be%20built%20for%20a%20more%20resilient%20information%20ecosystem%20that%20upholds%20the%20integrity%20of%20democratic%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEveryone%20has%20a%20role%20to%20play%20in%20fighting%20this%20menace%2C%20by%20verifying%20and%20reviewing%20where%20they%20get%20their%20information%2C%20by%20ensuring%20that%20they%20don't%20share%20falsehoods%2C%20and%20by%20investing%20in%20trustworthy%20media.%C2%A0%20The%20path%20leading%20to%20combating%20mis-and%20disinformation%20is%20going%20to%20require%20all%20of%20us.%C2%A0%20It%20is%20a%20big%20and%20long%20global%20fight.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20valuable%20lessons%20we%20learned%20from%20the%20Shakti%20Collective%20is%20that%20when%20we%20want%20to%20encourage%20people%20to%20do%20something%20big%2C%20we%20need%20to%20make%20it%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESyed%20Nazakat%20is%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20DataLEADS%2C%20a%20New%20Delhi-based%2C%20award-winning%2C%20globally%20recognized%20digital%20media%20and%20tech%20company%20spearheading%20a%20series%20of%20fact-checking%2C%20digital%20safety%2C%20and%20information%20literacy%20initiatives.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722668040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https