Anmol%20Bishnoi%2C%20the%20brother%20of%20the%20incarcerated%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%2C%20and%20the%20shooters%20involved.%20A%209-minute-long%20speech%20by%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%20was%20aimed%20at%20instilling%20courage%20in%20the%20shooters%2C%20Vicky%20Gupta%20and%20Sagar%20Pal%2C%20as%20they%20prepared%20to%20%26quot%3Bscript%20history%26quot%3B%20with%20their%20violent%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20night%20of%20April%2014%2C%20Mumbai's%20Bandra%20neighbourhood%20was%20rocked%20by%20the%20sound%20of%20gunfire%20as%20two%20men%20on%20motorbikes%20fired%20multiple%20rounds%20outside%20Salman%20Khan's%20residence.%20This%20brazen%20attack%20led%20to%20a%20swift%20police%20response%20and%20the%20subsequent%20arrest%20of%20several%20individuals%20linked%20to%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnmol%20Bishnoi's%20Speech%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nine-minute%20audio%20clip%20begins%20with%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%20giving%20a%20pep%20talk%2C%20with%20religious%20references%2C%20to%20the%20shooters.%20%26quot%3BLord%20Ram%20has%20blessed%20us.%20We%20will%20handle%20(Salman%20Khan)%20him.%20There%20is%20no%20problem%2C%20as%20long%20as%20it%20is%20in%20my%20control%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20it%20is%20do%20or%20die%2C%20either%20life%20or%20death.%20It%20is%20written%20by%20God.%20Either%20the%20bullets%20will%20be%20fired%20in%20the%20morning%20or%20we%20will%20sit%20at%20home.%20It%20is%20in%20your%20hands%20what%20to%20do%20and%20what%20not%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%20said.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BIf%20you%20work%2C%20then%20history%20will%20be%20created.%20You%20will%20fill%20the%20newspapers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20chargesheet%2C%20the%20plan%20was%20hatched%20over%20several%20months%2C%20from%20August%202023%20to%20April%202024.%20Investigations%20have%20revealed%20that%20the%20gang%20intended%20to%20acquire%20advanced%20firearms%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20including%20AK-47s%2C%20AK-92s%2C%20M16%20rifles%2C%20and%20the%20Turkish-made%20Zigana%20pistol%2C%20the%20weapon%20used%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20Punjabi%20singer%20Sidhu%20Moose%20Wala%20on%20May%2029%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20be%20afraid%20at%20all%20while%20doing%20this%20work.%20Doing%20this%20work%20means%20bringing%20change%20in%20the%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%20said.%20He%20told%20the%20shooters%20that%20the%20Bishnoi%20Gang%20had%20a%20signature%20move.%20According%20to%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%2C%20whenever%20the%20gang%20attempts%20a%20killing%2C%20they%20empty%20the%20magazine%20of%20the%20gun.%20%26quot%3BYou%20people%20will%20empty%20the%20magazine%20as%20soon%20as%20you%20reach%20outside%20Salman%20Khan's%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Operation%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20chargesheet%2C%20a%20network%20of%20approximately%2060%20to%2070%20individuals%20was%20involved%20in%20tracking%20Mr%20Khan's%20every%20movement.%20This%20extensive%20surveillance%20covered%20his%20residence%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20his%20Panvel%20farmhouse%2C%20and%20even%20the%20Goregaon%20Film%20City%2C%20where%20he%20often%20visited%20for%20film%20shoots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chargesheet%20claims%20that%20boys%20below%20the%20age%20of%2018%20were%20recruited%20to%20execute%20the%20assassination.%20These%20minors%20were%20reportedly%20waiting%20for%20orders%20from%20Goldie%20Brar%20and%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20operating%20from%20North%20America%2C%20to%20initiate%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20a%20special%20court%20in%20Mumbai%20issued%20a%20non-bailable%20warrant%20(NBW)%20against%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%20and%20Rohit%20Godera%2C%20an%20alleged%20member%20of%20the%20Bishnoi%20gang.%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20is%20currently%20lodged%20in%20the%20Sabarmati%20central%20prison%20in%20Ahmedabad.%3