0give%20her%20all%20in%20the%20upcoming%20bout%2C%20vowing%20to%20%26quot%3Bfight%20as%20long%20as%20I%20can.%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20humble%20opinion%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20fair%20that%20this%20contestant%20can%20compete%20in%20the%20women's%20category.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20cannot%20concern%20myself%20with%20that%20now.%20I%20cannot%20change%20it%2C%20it's%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20promise%20you%20one%20thing...%20I%20will%20do%20my%20best%20to%20win%20and%20I%20will%20fight%20as%20long%20as%20I%20can!%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Hamori%20on%20%E2%80%98X'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhelif%2C%20along%20with%20Taiwan's%20Lin%20Yu-ting%2C%20was%20previously%20disqualified%20from%20last%20year's%20Women's%20World%20Championships%20after%20failing%20gender%20eligibility%20tests%20conducted%20by%20the%20Russia-led%20International%20Boxing%20Association%20(IBA).%20The%20IBA%20had%20stripped%20both%20athletes%20of%20their%20medals%20and%20barred%20them%20from%20participating%20in%20the%20women's%20competition%20to%20maintain%20fairness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20both%20boxers%20have%20now%20been%20cleared%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20Olympics%2C%20as%20the%20International%20Olympic%20Committee%20(IOC)%20bases%20gender%20eligibility%20on%20the%20athlete's%20passport%20gender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hungarian%20Boxing%20Association%20and%20the%20Hungarian%20Olympic%20Committee%20have%20protested%20against%20Khelif's%20participation%2C%20demanding%20discussions%20with%20the%20IOC%20over%20the%20matter.%20They%20argue%20that%20the%20inclusion%20of%20Khelif%20in%20the%20women's%20category%20undermines%20the%20principle%20of%20equal%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBulgarian%20boxer%20Svetlana%20Kamenova%20Staneva%2C%20who%20will%20face%20Lin%20in%20her%20quarter-final%20match%2C%20expressed%20her%20concerns%20about%20the%20fairness%20of%20the%20competition.%20Staneva%2C%20supported%20by%20the%20Bulgarian%20Boxing%20Federation%2C%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20equal%20treatment%20and%20criticised%20the%20situation%20for%20casting%20a%20shadow%20over%20women's%20boxing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhelif's%20presence%20in%20the%20tournament%20has%20also%20sparked%20controversy%20beyond%20the%20athletes'%20circle.%20Kheireddine%20Barbari%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Algerian%20delegation%2C%20condemned%20the%20campaign%20against%20Khelif%20as%20%26quot%3Bimmoral%26quot%3B%20and%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20IOC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IOC%2C%20having%20stripped%20the%20IBA%20of%20its%20status%20as%20the%20sport's%20world%20governing%20body%20last%20June%2C%20is%20now%20at%20the%20center%20of%20a%20complex%20dispute.%20The%20organisation%20has%20defended%20its%20decision%2C%20stating%20that%20Khelif%20and%20Lin%20were%20disqualified%20without%20due%20process%20by%20the%20IBA%20and%20highlighting%20that%20they%20are%20eligible%20to%20compete%20based%20on%20their%20passports.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722661800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fmoq818oo_dsa_625x300_03_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fimane-khelifs-next-opponent-makes-explosive-remark-ahead-of-paris-olympics-2024-bout-6252950%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hungarian%20boxer%20Anna%20Luca%20Hamori%20expressed%20her%20discontent%20about%20facing%20Algerian%20opponent%20Imane%20Khelif%20in%20the%20quarter-finals%20of%20the%2066%20kg%20boxing%20competition%20in%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fimane-khelifs-next-opponent-makes-explosive-remark-ahead-of-paris-olympics-2024-bout-6252950%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fimane-khelifs-next-opponent-makes-explosive-remark-ahead-of-paris-olympics-2024-bout-6252950%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fs