are%20still%20missing%20and%20six%20bodies%20were%20recovered%20so%20far%20as%20on%20Saturday%20after%20a%20cloudburst%20followed%20by%20flashfloods%20wreaked%20widespread%20destruction%20in%20Kullu%2C%20Mandi%20and%20Shimla%20regions%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20as%20per%20the%20District%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecial%20Secretary%20DC%20Rana%20of%20the%20DDMA%20said%20that%20over%20sixty%20houses%20were%20washed%20away%20and%20several%20villages%20have%20been%20severely%20affected%20by%20the%20floods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERestoration%20works%20are%20underway%20in%20Rampur%20where%20the%20cloudburst%20and%20following%20flashfloods%20damaged%20a%20road%20that%20connected%20Rampur%20and%20Samej%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722659940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fqretktbo_himachal-cloudburst-rampur_625x300_03_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fentire-village-washed-away-in-himachal-cloudburst-just-1-house-remains-6252923%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20recent%20cloudburst%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20has%20wrought%20devastating%20destruction%2C%20leaving%20an%20entire%20village%20obliterated.%20In%20the%20midst%20of%20this%20catastrophe%2C%20Anita%20Devi%20from%20the%20village%20of%20Samej%20shared%20her%20heart-wrenching%20story%2C%20highlighting%20the%20severity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fentire-village-washed-away-in-himachal-cloudburst-just-1-house-remains-6252923%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fentire-village-washed-away-in-himachal-cloudburst-just-1-house-remains-6252923%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fentire-village-washed-away-in-himachal-cloudburst-just-1-house-remains-6252923%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20Pow