der.com%2Fai-data-centers-us-power-grid-gpu-nvidia-cerebras-amazon-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20real%20estate%2C%20chips%20and%20other%20gear%20to%20build%20AI%20models%2C%20tools%20and%20products.%20That%20is%20only%20going%20to%20pay%20off%20if%20there's%20actual%20demand%20for%20these%20offerings%20from%20real%20users%2C%20especially%20corporate%20customers%20with%20money%20to%20spend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CIO%20story%20is%20not%20a%20good%20sign%20of%20strong%20demand.%20As%20Ashley%20wrote%2C%20if%20a%20pharma%20company%20can't%20spend%20an%20extra%20%24180%2C000%20on%20these%20AI%20tools%2C%20that's%20a%20problem%20for%20the%20entire%20tech%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20tech%20executives%20were%20peppered%20with%20questions%20on%20this%20broad%20topic%20during%20earnings%20calls%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20an%20industry%20debate%20raging%20around%20the%20capex%20requirements%20around%20generative%20AI%20and%20whether%20the%20monetization%20is%20actually%20going%20to%20match%20with%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Keith%20Weiss%2C%20a%20tech%20analyst%20at%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20said%20during%20the%20Microsoft%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20big%20tech%20companies%20have%20already%20whittled%20away%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20their%20cash%20reserves%20chasing%20this%20AI%20trend.%20Weiss%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20Wall%20Street%20wants%20to%20know%20the%20return%20on%20this%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20more%20than%20a%20year%2C%20the%20assumption%20has%20been%20that%20generative%20AI%20will%20stoke%20a%20massive%20wave%20of%20new%20demand.%20What%20if%20that%20demand%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20weaker%20than%20expected%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2226e46f8e-a8b7-432e-a08a-c37d78fe53f3%5C%22%3EThe%20perils%20of%20over-investing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%20that%20building%20lots%20of%20expensive%20data%20centers%20is%20a%20long-term%20commitment.%20If%20you%20end%20up%20not%20needing%20all%20that%20infrastructure%2C%20you%20can't%20just%20make%20it%20magically%20disappear.%20Those%20are%20very%20large%20costs%20that%20are%20mostly%20fixed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20CEO%20Andy%20Jassy%20put%20it%20well%20on%20his%20company's%20earnings%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20end%20up%20actually%20with%20too%20little%20capacity%2C%20then%20you%20have%20service%20disruptions%2C%20which%20really%20nobody%20does%20because%20it%20means%20companies%20can't%20scale%20their%20applications.%20So%20most%20companies%20deliver%20more%20capacity%20than%20they%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20if%20you%20actually%20deliver%20too%20much%20capacity%2C%20the%20economics%20are%20pretty%20woeful%20and%20you%20don't%20like%20the%20returns%20of%20the%20operating%20income.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Google%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20was%20asked%20a%20similar%20question%2C%20he%20said%20Google%20will%20choose%20over-investing%2C%20rather%20than%20miss%20out%20on%20potential%20AI%20revenue%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20risk%20of%20under-investing%20is%20dramatically%20greater%20than%20the%20risk%20of%20over-investing%20for%20us%20here%2C%20even%20in%20scenarios%20where%20if%20it%20turns%20out%20that%20we%20are%20over-investing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20is%20a%20%242%20trillion%20corporation%2C%20with%20oodles%20of%20data%20at%20its%20fingertips.%20I%20suspect%20that%20investors%20want%20the%20company%20to%20get%20this%20right%2C%20rather%20than%20over-invest%20and%20end%20up%20with%20woeful%20economics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227f4833dd-9b9f-4971-a88b-7639afc4035c%5C%22%3ENadella%20and%20365%20Copilot%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella%20was%20probably%20the%20most%20sanguine%20of%20all.%20He%20said%20the%20software%20giant%20is%20seeing%20strong%20demand%20signals%20from%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20major%20piece%20of%20evidence%20he%20shared%20was%20ab