tored%20glory%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20project%20completion%2C%20it%20was%20observed%20that%20the%20seasonal%20Sot%20river%20received%20ample%20water%20in%20the%20monsoon%20and%20remained%20rejuvenated%20for%20the%20next%20two%20and%20a%20half%20months.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20project%2C%20several%20micro%20check%20dams%20were%20also%20built%20on%20the%20river%20to%20slow%20the%20runoff%20in%20the%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20this%20work%20was%20lauded%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20his%20monthly%20radio%20programme%20%E2%80%98Mann%20Ki%20Baat%E2%80%99%20in%20September%202023.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20proved%20to%20be%20very%20encouraging%20for%20all%20the%20officials%20and%20%3Cem%3Egram%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%20associated%20with%20the%20project.%20Inspired%20by%20this%2C%20the%20districts%20of%20Amroha%20and%20Budaun%20also%20undertook%20the%20project%20of%20reviving%20the%20Sot%20river%20downstream%20and%20upstream%2C%20respectively%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Manish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-3-1722403565.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Within%20six%20months%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20revived%20the%20river%20to%20its%20old%20glory.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-3-1722403565.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-3-1722403565-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-3-1722403565-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-3-1722403565-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-3-1722403565-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-