nly%20when%20the%20community%20becomes%20the%20protector%20of%20its%20rivers%20that%20they%20can%20remain%20rejuvenated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Manish%2C%20the%20Sot%20river%20rejuvenation%20project%20during%20his%20tenure%20in%20Sambhal%20was%20extremely%20fulfilling.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20project%20was%20very%20close%20to%20my%20heart.%20Projects%20such%20as%20river%20rejuvenation%20take%20a%20backseat%20as%20they%20are%20not%20always%20a%20priority%20among%20other%20routine%20works.%20But%20if%20we%20do%20not%20rejuvenate%20these%20rivers%2C%20people%20will%20face%20the%20brunt%20of%20a%20water%20crisis.%20Thankfully%2C%20the%20State%20Government%20has%20also%20been%20actively%20focusing%20on%20the%20environment%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F230547%2Fias-hero-kalyani-river-cleanup-uttar-pradesh-lockdown-jobs-methods-workers-inspiring-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereviving%20water%20bodies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20establishing%20Amrit%20Sarovar%20projects%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Ram%20Ashish.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722426607000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-2-1722402541.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D359103%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sot%20River%2C%20once%20the%20lifeline%20of%20Sambhal%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20lost%20its%20natural%20flow%20due%20to%20decades%20of%20encroachment.%20Here's%20how%20IAS%20Manish%20Bansal%2C%20along%20with%20officials%20and%20locals%2C%20revived%20the%20110-km%20stretch%2C%20restoring%20water%20flow%20and%20eliminating%20waterlogging.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359103%2Fias-officer-sot-river-revival-rejuvenation-project-sambhal-uttar-pradesh-manish-bansal-m