0secret%20recipes%2C%20they%20show%20how%20senior%20citizens%20can%20start%20new%20ventures%20and%20thrive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358385%2Findian-grandmothers-running-food-ventures-businesses-pickles-chutneys-snacks-senior-citizen%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Started%20Swimming%20at%2045%20%26amp%3B%20Became%20an%20International%20Champion%20at%2063%E2%80%99%3A%20Meet%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Iron%20Lady%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20small%20village%20in%20Golaghat%2C%20Assam%2C%20a%20girl%20with%20extraordinary%20prowess%20was%20born%20in%201962.%20Fourth%20amongst%20five%20siblings%2C%20she%20had%20an%20idyllic%20childhood%20that%20involved%20a%20lot%20of%20play%20with%20her%20brothers%20and%20sisters.%20One%20could%20spot%20Ranjita%20Gogoi%20hopping%2C%20skipping%2C%20jumping%20and%20running%20around%20all%20the%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20school%20and%20college%20too%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331500%2Fneeru-yadav-hockeywali-sarpanch-rajasthan-kbc-hockey-women-patriarchy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshe%20excelled%20in%20sports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20becoming%20the%20volleyball%20captain%20and%20participating%20in%20various%20inter-collegiate%20sports.%20However%2C%20sports%20took%20a%20backseat%20after%20life%20and%20different%20priorities%20took%20over%20post%20marriage.%20One%20thing%20that%20remained%20constant%20throughout%20her%20life%20though%20was%20going%20to%20her%20gym.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20turning%20point%20that%20transformed%20this%20mother%20of%20two%20into%20a%20champion%20was%20the%20inauguration%20of%20a%20swimming%20pool%20in%202011.%20Ever%20ready%20for%20a%20challenge%2C%20Ranjita%2C%20who%20was%20then%20in%20her%20late%2040s%2C%20dove%20into%20the%20pool%2C%20which%20for%20her%2C%20brimmed%20with%20possibilities.%20Soon%2C%20she%20started%20competing%20in%20district%2C%20state%2C%20national%20and%20international%20level%20competitions%2C%20emerging%20victorious%20each%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEntranced%20by%20the%20world%20of%20competitive%20sports%2C%20she%20then%20tried%20her%20hand%20at%20powerlifting%20and%20arm%20wrestling%20too.%20The%20result%20%E2%80%94%20just%20as%20you%20expected%20%E2%80%94%20earned%20her%20the%20title%20of%20%E2%80%98Iron%20Lady%20of%20Assam%E2%80%99%20at%20the%20state%20level.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20incredibly%20proud%20of%20her.%20I%20remember%20the%20first%20time%20she%20won%20a%20competition%20in%20swimming.%20It%20was%20sometime%20in%202013-14%20and%20we%20threw%20a%20big%20party%20for%20her%20with%20all%20relatives%20and%20friends.%20They%20all%20were%20so%20proud%20of%20her%20and%20wanted%20her%20to%20continue%20and%20achieve%20bigger%20things.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20the%20happiest%20I%20had%20ever%20seen%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20her%20son%20Anjumon%2C%20his%20voice%20brimming%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%E2%80%99ve%20always%20heard%20parents%20speak%20about%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20achievements.%20It%E2%80%99s%20pleasantly%20surprising%20when%20the%20tables%20are%20turned%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%2062-year-old%20Ranjita%E2%80%99s%20inspiring%20tale%20of%20achieving%20her%20dreams%2C%20age%20no%20bar!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20down%20a%20government%20job%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20a%20Bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%20(BSc)%20in%20agriculture%2C%20Ranjita%20got%20a%20government%20job.%20Post%20marriage%2C%20she%20shifted%20to%20a%20nearby%20district%20of%20Jorhat%2C%20where%20she%20continued%20her%20service.%20She%20then%20moved%20to%20the%20Philippines%20for%20a%20few%20years%20for%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20PhD%20degree.%20Always%20eager%20to%20learn%2C%20