%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20almost%20like%20an%20inferiority%20complex.%20While%20everyone%20enjoyed%20themselves%2C%20I%20was%20stuck%20in%20the%20sidelines.%20Couples%20swam%20together%20while%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20join%20my%20husband%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ranjita%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20in%20the%20early%2090s%20and%20after%20they%20returned%20to%20India%2C%20the%20swimming%20dream%20remained%20unfulfilled%20as%20there%20was%20no%20swimming%20pool%20nearby.%20By%20the%20time%2C%20their%20family%20too%20had%20grown%20and%20Ranjita%20juggled%20motherhood%20with%20her%20job.%20However%2C%20she%20had%20to%20quit%20in%20a%20few%20years%2C%20a%20regret%20which%20haunts%20Anjumon%20till%20date.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20in%20nursery%20school%20and%20would%20miss%20my%20mom%20after%20coming%20back%20home.%20I%20would%20cry%20and%20tell%20her%20to%20be%20at%20home%20due%20to%20which%20she%20quit%20her%20job%20and%20never%20joined%20back.%20I%20regret%20it%20even%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanjita%20kept%20herself%20busy%20tending%20to%20her%20beautiful%20garden%2C%20a%20hobby%20that%20she%20continues%20even%20today%20amidst%20her%20hectic%20schedule.%20She%20was%20soon%20kept%20busier%20by%20another%20addition%20to%20the%20family%2C%20Anjumon%E2%80%99s%20brother.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20harboured%20an%20ambition%20to%20move%20up%20in%20life%20and%20looked%20for%20avenues%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20champion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatience%20is%20rewarding%2C%20as%20an%20opportunity%20presented%20itself%20when%20a%20Swimming%20Federation%20of%20India%20(SFI)%20pool%20opened%20in%20Jorhat%20in%202011.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20she%20started%20swimming%2C%20first%20as%20a%20daily%20routine%20and%20soon%2C%20competitively.%20Despite%20the%20late%20start%2C%20her%20dedication%20paid%20off%20remarkably%20as%20she%20quickly