and%20courage.%20Every%20morning%2C%20even%20before%20her%20mother%20awakens%2C%20she%20finishes%20cooking%20and%20cleaning%20before%20cycling%205%20km%20from%20her%20house%20in%20Risia%20block%E2%80%99s%20Chhitan%20Purva%20village%20to%20run%20her%20shop%20alone.%20It%20is%20this%20indomitable%20spirit%20and%20determination%20that%20has%20helped%20Rachna%20follow%20her%20dreams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20aspirational%20district%20with%20low%20socio-economic%20indicators%20where%20girls%20are%20married%20soon%20after%20reaching%20puberty%2C%20Rachna%20too%2C%20would%20have%20met%20the%20same%20fate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20to%20drop%20out%20of%20school%20due%20to%20family%E2%80%99s%20financial%20constraints%2C%20she%20resisted%20early%20marriage%20and%20dared%20to%20pursue%20her%20dreams%20to%20become%20an%20artist%20and%20an%20entrepreneur.%20Over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20she%20has%20sold%20about%20200%20of%20her%20paintings%2C%2050%20of%20which%20were%20bought%20since%20she%20opened%20her%20shop%20in%20April%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20she%20achieved%20this%20admirable%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20opportunities%20make%20dreams%20come%20true%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202019%2C%20Rachna%20had%20almost%20given%20up%20on%20life.%20%E2%80%9CI%20became%20depressed%20after%20dropping%20out.%20I%20thought%20I%20would%20have%20to%20spend%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20days%20doing%20household%20chores.%20As%20the%20eldest%20of%20five%20siblings%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20me%20to%20get%20married%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Rachna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20this%20time%2C%20the%20Aga%20Khan%20Foundation%20(AKF)%20came%20into%20the%20picture%20with%20Project%20Lehar.%20Started%20to%20provide%20vocational%20training%2C%20entrepreneurship%2C%20and%20life%20skills%20courses%20to%20marginalised%20young%20women%2C%20Project%20Lehar%2C%20run%20by%20AKF%20in%20