l%202024%3A%20Siblings%20With%20AIR%201%20and%2018%20Share%20Preparation%20Tips%2C%20Planning%20Secrets%20%26amp%3B%20More%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20can%20be%20divided%20into%20two%20sets%20of%20people%3A%20those%20who%20like%20to%20study%20alone%20and%20those%20who%20prefer%20a%20study%20buddy.%20I%20fall%20into%20the%20latter%20category%2C%20as%20having%20someone%20in%20the%20same%20boat%20as%20you%20to%20motivate%20you%20and%20answer%20your%20queries%20is%20a%20boon.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20fun%2C%20as%20you%20have%20someone%20to%20discuss%20doubts%20with%20during%20break%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20if%20this%20study%20buddy%20lived%20in%20the%20same%20house%E2%80%94your%20sibling%3F%20This%20is%20usually%20a%20rarity%20unless%20the%20sibling%20is%20a%20twin%2C%20but%20these%20siblings%20from%20Morena%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20a%20shining%20example%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349546%2Fakshata-krishnamurthy-nasa-aerospace-engineer-rocket-scientist-space-career-mit%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheights%20that%20can%20be%20achieved%20together.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESachin%20(24)%20and%20Nandini%20(22)%20Agrawal%2C%20although%20two%20years%20apart%2C%20were%20in%20the%20same%20class%20since%20Class%202.%20Nandini%20skipped%20two%20classes%20and%20joined%20her%20brother%20in%20his%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20paths%20intertwined%20as%20they%20decided%20on%20a%20singular%20goal%3A%20to%20add%20two%20letters%20before%20their%20name%20%E2%80%94%20CA%20(Chartered%20Accountant).%20The%20duo%20worked%20together%20towards%20achieving%20this%20goal%2C%20choosing%20the%20same%20coaching%20class%20and%20the%20same%20city%20for%20their%20articleships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20efforts%20paid%20off%2C%20and%20how!%20Both%20of%20them%20achieved%20ranks%20in%20the%20CA%20Final%20in%202021.%20The%20icing%20on%20the%20cake%20w